<h2 class="bold font-l">Eris, the Goddess of Discord</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
As a chaos goddess, Eris constantly shifts her form. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PerpetuallyProtean" class='trope-example-link'>Perpetually Protean</a></p>
</div>
